                                    <h4 class="font-weight-bold pt-0 pb-3">Drawdown Plugin</h4>
                                    <p>Drawdown Limit is a plugin for MetaTrader 5 platform that sets equity limits for trading accounts. When the equity limit is reached, the plugin closes all open positions of the trading account and restricts the ability to trade. The plugin is needed to prevent an excessive equity loss or equity growth on the trading account.</p>
